# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Update the camera configurations with your actual camera details
# 3. Adjust feature flags and confidence thresholds as needed
# 4. Never commit your .env file to version control

# Feature Options:
# - human_detection: Enable/disable human detection for this camera
# - person_identification: Enable/disable person identification (future feature)
# - sound_alert: Enable/disable sound alerts for detections
# - confidence_threshold: Detection confidence threshold (0.0 to 1.0)